Privacy Policy for ATLAS AI
Effective Date: 13/11/2024

This Privacy Policy explains how ATLAS AI collects, uses, and protects your information. By using ATLAS AI, you consent to the practices outlined below.

1. Information We Collect

Personal Information: We collect personal data you provide, such as your name, email address, and payment details for premium features.
Device Information: We collect device and technical information, including IP addresses, device IDs, and usage statistics, to enhance functionality and security.
Usage Data: We collect interactions within ATLAS AI to improve service accuracy and personalization.
2. How We Use Your Information We use your information to:

Provide and maintain ATLAS AI services;
Enhance user experience through personalized content;
Improve AI responses based on user interactions;
Communicate with you regarding updates, promotions, or support requests;
Conduct research and analysis to improve ATLAS AI.
3. Sharing and Disclosure of Information We do not sell your personal data to third parties. We may share your information with:

Service Providers: Trusted third parties assisting in service delivery, such as payment processing and technical support.
Legal Obligations: If required by law or legal processes, we may disclose your information to comply with governmental requests.
Protection of Rights: We may share information to protect the rights, property, or safety of ATLAS AI users, or in response to potential misuse of our platform.
4. Data Security We implement industry-standard measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, misuse, or loss. Despite these efforts, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

5. Data Retention We retain personal information as long as it is necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. You may request deletion of your data, subject to any legal or operational retention requirements.

6. User Rights You have the right to:

Access and review the data we collect about you;
Request corrections to inaccurate or incomplete information;
Delete or restrict processing of your data under certain conditions;
Withdraw consent for data collection or processing where applicable.
7. Cookies and Tracking ATLAS AI uses cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance user experience, analyze trends, and collect data on how the service is used. You can control cookie settings through your browser.

8. Third-Party Links ATLAS AI may contain links to external sites not controlled by us. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party sites.

9. Childrenâ€™s Privacy Our services are intended for users over the age of 18. We do not knowingly collect or solicit information from children under 18. If we learn of unauthorized data collection from minors, we will take steps to delete that information promptly.

10. Changes to this Privacy Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage users to review it periodically for any changes. Continued use of ATLAS AI following updates indicates your acceptance of the revised policy.

11. Contact Us For questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or your data rights, please contact us at zafir.buy@gmail.com.
